{
  "stem": "26465.3",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So the-- the Gestapo-- the kapo would come with the-- with the whip and whip us up, and, or push us in-- I remember I was once pushed right into the wall.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Because I stood in front of the wall, thinking I was supposed to clean that wall that was full of filth.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Somebody was probably tortured against that wall.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "There was blood and dirt and feces.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And I was to clean that.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And I was hesitating, standing there, and that man came right there to me, and he banged me right into the wall, into that-- into that dirt.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And-- and my face was bleeding and soiled.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And I just couldn't just come to myself.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And I was excusing myself and begging-- in Polish, of course.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "I didn't know my German.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And, of course, that got on his nerves.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "He even pushed me again, and so on and that.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "So finally I cleaned that wall.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And I remember I came-- came back to the barrack.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And I was bringing up, and I was very, very upset and quite a-- this is one of many incidents that we had.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And quite everybody, every day, brought some-- some account of terrible story-- terrible happening to her, in that place.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And what really struck me was the great friendship and solidarity between those people.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "Somebody got hurt, the other women would come and would console-- would [INAUDIBLE] next to you.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "The Jewish people-- the Jewish women were in a different barrack.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "Because they sorted us out when we came, as you know, for the roll call.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And also I remember-- also, I forgot to tell you that, when we came first there we had-- we were all shaven.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And we were given this silly kerchiefs everybody wear-- had to wear.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
